<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/12 Saturday Articles 1 &amp; 2 : &quot;Horoscope &amp; personality traits&quot;, and &quot;Superpower&quot;  hosted by Ken]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=64&amp;p=68#p68"><![CDATA[
Article 1 : Horoscope &amp; personality traits. <br /><br />The topic for this Saturday is not difficult. It doesn't take a long time to prepare. Just look up some new words in your dictionary. <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://media-cache-ec0.pinimg.com/1200x/9e/25/5a/9e255a600d34c949146691292c8ae714.jpg">https://media-cache-ec0.pinimg.com/1200 ... 8ae714.jpg</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion: <br />Q1. What's your birthday and star sign?<br />Q2. What are the positive and negative qualities of your star sign?<br />Q3. Do you believe in horoscope? Why or why not?<br />Q4. Are you into other forms of fortune telling, such as Chinese zodiac signs, tarot cards, face reading or palm reading ?<br />Q5. Have you ever been to a fortune teller? Would you like to share the experience?<br /><br />========================================================================================================<br />Article 2: Superpower<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qU08IUUAod8">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qU08IUUAod8</a><!-- m --><br />（You can change closed caption language on YouTube ）<br /><br />Discussions:<br />Q1.If you could have one superpower, what would it be? <br />Q2. If you were a superhero or supervillain, what would you do?<br />Q3. Who is your favorite superhero or villain? Why do you like him or her?<br />Q4. What is your favorite superhero movie franchise? <br />Q5. Why are superhero or anti-hero movies so popular?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Fri Aug 11, 2017 12:40 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
